                <td bgcolor="#791212" class="copy"><p><img src="../images/img_specials.jpg" width="147" height="200" class="right">Treat 
                    yourself to one of our special all-inclusive packages - a 
                    leisurely day on the greens, a luxuriating day at the spa, 
                    a shopping spree at the mall or a Bay Area renowned Art &amp; 
                    Wine Festival. We've designed these special packages 
                    to help you relax, rejuvenate and experience the culture and 
                    character of Palo Alto, the Bay Area and exciting local destinations.</p>
                  <p> With these packages, guests can enjoy our new continental-style 
                    breakfast every morning at Coupa Caf&eacute;, a Latin-American 
                    caf&eacute; and wine / Prosecco bar located four doors down 
                    from the hotel on Ramona. Coupa Caf&eacute; promises to take 
                    coffee to a new level. Experience Latin America's finest 
                    coffee imported from Venezuela served in an architecturally 
                    beautiful setting, with richly colored paint, an exquisite 
                    tiled floor from the 1930s, cozy seating in front of a fully 
                    restored fireplace, and a magnificent granite bar with tiles 
                    imported from Latin America. At Coupa Caf&eacute; everything 
                    is first class from the ingredients in their paninni to their 
                    case of imported Belgian chocolates made from Venezuelan cacao.</p>
